Lupin Gets Approval From FDA for Generic Levetiracetam Syrup

-- B y   A d i   N a r a y a n
-- 
2011-10-19T03:17:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-19/lupin-gets-approval-from-fda-for-generic-levetiracetam-syrup.html
Lupin Ltd. (LPC) , an Indian drugmaker,
received approval from the U.S. Food and Drug Administration for
its levetiracetam oral syrup, the generic version of  UCB SA (UCB) ’s
Keppra anti-epilepsy medicine, according to a statement on the
regulator’s website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Adi Narayan in Mumbai at 
